  (
  'Polo (Uyghur Pilaf)',
  'Main dish',
  'Chinese',
  'Heat oil in a large pot. Fry the meat until browned, then add onions and cook until golden. Add carrots and stir-fry for a few minutes. Season with salt, cumin, and black pepper. Add water and bring to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer until meat is tender. Add washed rice evenly on top without stirring, place the whole garlic in the center, and pour water to cover the rice slightly. Cover and cook on low heat until rice absorbs water and becomes tender. Gently mix before serving.',
